{"text": "This game if i were to express it in two words i'd say masterclass and bittersweet. Valve did a good job on combining comedy and action with the unique graphics and mechanics in the game -The boston boyscout who literally wont even leave you alone-GOOD LORD CAN SOMEONE FIND A FITTING HELMET FOR THIS MAN-it is been 13 years and we still don't even know who is person is-Alcoholic black scottish cyclops with a grenade launcher forces you to pray for a hit-A russian fugitive who currently lives in siberia to get away from the soviet union -A texan engineer who has a ♥♥♥♥ off huge guns -Australian version of florida man who thinks that throwing a jar of piss at everyone is an efficient way to combat against your adversary -A nazi who made a deal with literal satan and yet holds a head of a frenchman as a hostage -A baguette choking frenchman who is being played by all weebs in the worldThese kind of character make you laugh at their personality while causing a mass homicide in the battlefields. the game offers you a many various playstyle such as a demoknight and pybros. The community is a literal gem they are bunch of different good personalities there. there are things make me feel irritated about this game is that the game has lack of updates because of valve doesn't even want to update the game and secondly the current state of the game in 2020 the source code has been leaked which resulting in increasing amount of hackers and bot users right now the game is in need of security update as soon as possible but luckily the community vote the bots off as soon as they join the server. in conclusion fun game i've been playing the game since i was 6th grade i'll give it solid 8.5/10  Fun gameplay, diverse playstyles, and unique graphics but valve is a total nuisance when it comes to updating been a while since the game last updated so there is lack of content and there is no actions taken against bots and hackers until this day", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profil