{"text": "This game is great. Tracks look slick, AI is pretty good, cars and environments look amazing and the weather system is truly something to behold. Driving during a summer storm, wet tracks and puddles that will make you spin out in the corners; it just feels so real and visceral.  It's a racing sim that will allow you to have fun while learning the behaviour of the cars on mostly real life tracks. You can also just get the car you like and cruise the Azure coast or Cali highway in single player. The community seems nice and helpful too. I play with a G25 setup and I do single player as well as online multiplayer races.", "appid": "378860", "steamid": "profiles/76561197989605410", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579348800.0}
