{"text": "Game is hella fun, no P2W mechanics here (aka no paid only weapons or planes).  You can pay to get extra slots to have more then 2 active planes.  Death resets the plane and any upgrades you have on it (and anything in the cargohold of the plane), however pilot XP remains forever.  The game is perfectly playable F2P wise, you will need to be more careful as to what you save via storage (can be a klepto).  Its an Open World top down bullet hell shooter so fighting a boss can be alone, or have a bunch of players randomly show up to help.  The game is entirely PVE so other players aren't a negitive when doing something difficult.", "appid": "386010", "steamid": "profiles/76561197978815095", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1566907200.0}
