{"text": "Laser Leauge is a came of thrills chaos and tyrany. If you want to play an awesome game of dodgeball this is your game as this is the most enduring sport of this year (Although it is still in beta) The Lighting and surrounding of the map is immense and immersive drawing you into the game as your eyes get entranced by the obsticals of the arena, as this is an open beta there probably will be flaws that will show upon playing however I have yet not see any issue in these begining stages of development. The game has several styles of play and abilities to try help you survive through the laser course of dances you may endure, If you think you know the map, Think again as it changes and terriefies the life out of you when a powerup changes the polarity of the game It will keep you on the edge of your toes wondering what move to make and have everyone planning their next move with tactile and precise impact. But beware, time is short in an arena full of lasers! You may be surrounded by the Laser grid only for a team member to flip it to your teams colour helping you regain the high ground, You will endure a lot of frustration and enjoyment out of this game I would gladly give money when this is available as I have never been on the edge of a game as much as this. Rocket Leauge Take your Balls and Keep Them!", "appid": "730590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063256932", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517054400.0}
