{"text": "While reading other reviews, I see a lot of people that are extremely unhappy with the state of the game. While the game is obviously frustrating, and can lead to a lot of anger at times, I've felt that the game is really good for what it is. Don't expect too much because it is an Early Access game that came upon an insane amount of success for such a small game studio.  In my own personal experiences, I've met hackers, toxic people, experienced poor game performance due to optimization, and have died because of desync issues. Nevertheless, I've had a ton of fun playing this game, and I'm gonna keep having fun playing this game because I think it's fun as ♥♥♥♥ regardless of the issues that it has.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198133961264", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1511611200.0}
