{"text": "Creepiest game ever. Nothing says \"SPOOK ME BABY!\" quite like being a FRIGGIN KID with no reasoning skills that thinks that being shrunk on a backyard is \"cool\" and shiz while being CHASED by a GIANT FRIGGIN SPIDER! Bro forget Phasmophobia, Amnesia, Dead by Daylight (lol) or Visage. Nothing will make you SCREAM for mommy and daddy quite like seeing a gargantuan ladybug come unexpectadly next to you or a FREAKIN GODZILLA SPIDER two hit you by surprise and make sure you die an awful, gruesome death, prolly to be used as spidey baby food later. I love how the game has kinda cartoony graphics (they're great) but the devs went ALL OUT in making you feel like you're actually a tiny lil kid wandering around your backyard. I loathed every bug infested second of it. Nah who am I kidding. I loved it. But I WILL get the cops called on me if I keep screaming and shrieking at the sight of new gigantic bugs. I know I will. Lmao. 99/10 Flamthrowerin' my backyard after playing Grounded again. Thanks for the free weekend devs. <3", "appid": "962130", "steamid": "profiles/76561197966189515", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1605355200.0}
