{"text": "☑Great story for a 'What if'' Scenario with 2 different stories (Satsuki's & Ryuko's) ☑Amazing cast of characters pretty much all from the KLK anime minus Mako and the Nudists (which is coming as free DLC) ☑Combat is extremely fun & fast paced one of the better arena fighters, better than My Hero One's Justice but not as good as the Storm series ☑Animation is amazing all around in the story cutscenes, fight intros & supers that look straight out of an anime attack ☑Most of the boss fights are very enjoyable ☑Ragyō ☑Satsuki ☑Characters do not feel the same to play at all and are all very distinctive in gameplay styles ☑Has the anime OST which is GODLIKE ☑Characters are not censored and keep all of their anime sexiness ☒The final boss of Satsuki's story mode is a little underwhelming, but on the other hand Ryuko's final boss fight is decent ☒FPS is locked at 60, and sometimes especially in story or covers mode when lots of enemies surround you the frames drop ☒Crashes randomly, rarely happens has only happened to me twice ☒Not enough intriguing modes to keep players interested ☒No alternate costumes only 3 different colors which is a HUGE missed opportunity (especially for DLC) such as Ryuko in Junketsu or Satuski in Senketsu from the anime ☒For some reason they didn't choose Ragyō's original design even though its in the story mode ☒Some of the difficulty spikes are relatively hard in the story mode for bosses, though the difficulty can be changed ☒Price tag is a little too much but it has just came out at the time of writing this review, if it is still the same price as full release in a while I'd wait until its around 25% off or more in a sale Overall this is a very faithful game that is better than most of the anime arena fighters out there with the only expectation I can think of being the Storm series. Others like One's Justice or Burning Blood are very slow paced compared to this and bland so would definitely give it a shot if you haven't already 7/10 ‘Now, which of you will adorn my body today?’ ɪ ᴡᴀɴᴛ ʀᴀɢʏō ᴛᴏ sᴛᴇᴘ ᴏɴ ᴍᴇ", "appid": "922500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118979081", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1564228800.0}
