{"text": "This game is good, also for new players, its still fun to play. Just needed to find your own way or check some tips and tricks in youtube for better experience. EDIT: I ran out of fuel, and I thought I have no hope to survive. Then this group called Fuel Rats are still active, I saw their ads way way back 5 years ago in Reddit, and I've decided to contact them since I'm new to the game. The experience with their group is outstanding, they all ask professional questions and giving me helpful instructions to avoid death in the harsh space environment, and then the 2 commander arrived to save my ship and myself giving me fuel, repairs and everything in the galaxy that I needed in order to survive. The effort they gave is massively priceless. Not one of the best space game, but \"THE BEST SPACE GAME\" I've ever played with super awesome community.", "appid": "359320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198011992357", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602676800.0}
