{"text": "I love coming across an indie game expecting a good shooter and coming out of a gaming session realizing I have stumbled  across another gem. The amount of polish that has gone into the game is superb and shows from every corner. The UI is slick and beautiful, the weapons are diverse and the 2 weapon system gives the player a wide and constantly changing arsenal to use, the controller support is excellent (Using a Dualshock 4 + \"DS4 Windows\" Program), the game and its beautiful pixel style scales beautifully to many resolutions (Tested 1920x1080 and my native 2560x1440). All around a perfect and difficult but very fulfilling side-scrolling shooter that has blown away my expectations and is absolutely worth the money. Im in love ^u^", "appid": "347160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198034958524", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1432296000.0}
