{"text": "WARNING: This game is at least 12 years old. It got re-re-released so many times, i lost track of all the names this game & all the devs had. I know for sure, most recently this game was running under the name of \"Szone Online\" or \"Stalker Online\"  So, why the warning? - It's massive Pay2Win, go look for yourself if you're interested in this game. Just simply install it & open the game. You can see the pay2win being thrown in your face directly at the first screen. - This game is (i think) at least 12 years old & beside from a few cosmetic changes, never ever had this game any big content updates or remarkable changes. - It's from a russian (probably) scam company. I know of people who paid a lot of money for the last releases of the game (for example: Szone Online) & suddenly they shut it down with only a single e-mail being sent out to all the players & everything was gone. No compensation. Nothing. - Everything in this game is slow. It's too slow. It's made slow. From butchering animals, to reloading, to finishing the tutorial, making money, etc.... everything is made so slow, only for you to buy ♥♥♥♥ from the store. - This game is at the most an alpha. Theres so many bugs, glitches, errors, bad graphics, fps drops, etc... saying this is a 1.0 release, just because the devs say it, says nothing. - It's a russian game, sure, but they made enough money & theres enough people who played over the years that there should be a good english translation. but. as you probably already assume, theres NOT. most of the text ingame is very very bad english & everything is text, i cant even remember a single NPC speaking. Mostly impossible to find out what stuff means. - There was a wiki, but since the devs decide to change the name of the game every 2 years  & re-release it, change a few cosmetic things, the map  a little & etc... you know just to even make more money of this piece of an asset. Wiki's are mostly useless, anything's in russian anyways. What can i say - i somehow freaking love this game - there's nothing like this, which is coming sooo close to an S.T.A.L.K.E.R.-like mmorpg. Theres really nothing else. This game has really cool atmosphere & with the anomalies, mutants, radiation & stuff it really feels like a S.T.A.L.K.E.R. game, but be warned. Sure i want more english people on the US server. Getting a big clan with germans would be super awesome, as in the old times of Szone Online, but i aint lying to you guys, It is really bad, it's very frustrating & most probably even an absolute timewaste, because of moneywhoring greedy, incompetent devs.", "appid": "1180380", "steamid": "profiles/76561197987286350", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "274", "votes_funny": "10", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1578398400.0}
