{"text": "I have revisited the game with the mounts update. It is fun to find and lvl up the best NPC you can, and the new dungeons are really fun to do, the first couple of times. It does have some decent amount of lore to be found and there are no limits other than the end of the map itself. Now with this being said, it is still a massive grind with overall broken AI. Many times my own NPC gets in the way causing me to miss or get hit by the enemy. So all you do is sit back and watch, maybe pop some healing arrows every now and then. In pvp you need a clan or else you cant do ♥♥♥♥ because you have raid time and ofc every soul in the server is online in raid time, so good luck taking on other groups on your own, And that is a problem to me because I like to play the full game, and not farm to someone else to build and I already take orders in my job so clans are pretty much a fast way to dry up the game for me. I would like to see solo duo trio servers like in rust, and servers with no raid time. Also funcom needs to make it easyer to change stats on your char because it gets old really quick having to set up everything.. can i save a loadout or a set up or whatever you wana call it, and then take the potion and select it? Everything comes at a really slow rate in this game and to add insult into injury most of the new content is stuck behind payed DLCs and you will get huge advantages from them. All together is a 100€ game and doesnt feel that way to me. It does demand most of your time and I cant dedicate myself this much to a game. Specially when the developers take so long to add new stuff and demand money at every possible turn. My review is negative only because of the pay to win mechanica and the dumb AI and NPC mechanics. I have had 4 purges all spawn outside my base and just staying there, staring... lol, it is a joke for 2019 AI. But its emersive enough wile you r building yourself up. Just not 100€ worth, to me.", "appid": "440900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036769187", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496404800.0}
